metadata.name: AaP2023TTFPARTⅡ
metadata.description:
A group exhibition "AaP2023 Towards The Future" by AaP's next-generation artists will be held at roidworksgallery in Yushima.

Young artists who create works full of originality in various ways of expression and send messages to society.  
I hope that you can feel the great potential they have through their attractive works.

PART2: 2023年3月4日(土)-3月12日(日)
